    <scopecontent>
      <head>Scope and Contents</head>
      <p>The Troy, N.Y. United Calvary Congregational Church records include church record books,
        membership records, church correspondence, photograph collections, and anniversary reports.
        Also included are financial records, in the form of treasurer's records, receipts, and
        building records.</p>
    </scopecontent>
    <arrangement>
      <head>Arrangement</head>
      <p>Materials have been arranged in chronological order by start date, and further by relation
        when appropriate.</p>
    </arrangement>
